Note: This has only been tested with Ubuntu 18.04.1 LTS
Note: This is not an installer, you have to keep this folder if you want to play the game

1. Extract the content of "MagnAndCie.tar.gz" and open the terminal inside the extracted folder

2. Make the script executable
chmod +x MagnAndCie.sh

3. Run the script when you want to start the game
./MagnAndCie.sh